05:14.230 --> 05:16.107
-You doing all right?
               -No.

05:18.067 --> 05:19.652
Welcome, welcome, welcome.

05:19.694 --> 05:21.237
Michelle,
         great to see you.

05:21.279 --> 05:22.822
Thank you for having us.

05:22.864 --> 05:24.907
