I don't imagine it's
 an easy transition for anybody.

08:26.923 --> 08:29.091
Oh, of course.

08:29.133 --> 08:32.220
But the level of scrutiny
              on you,

08:32.970 --> 08:34.847
on your husband.

08:34.889 --> 08:38.893
